@page "/von"

<div class="demo-page">
    <div class="demo-page-shell">
        <section class="demo-hero">
            <p class="demo-kicker">SymAI Agent</p>
            <h1>Von</h1>
            <p class="demo-summary">
                Von is an autonomous general purpose agentic AI that runs reliably on a 24GB GPU.
                High end gaming machines have a 24GB GPU so Von is very cost effective to operate.
                Von is currently focused on GitHub bug fixing.
                Von can read your issues and deliver complete bug fixes for them with pull requests for $10/issue.
            </p>

            <div class="demo-notes">
                <div class="demo-note-card">
                    <h2>Quality over Quantity</h2>
                    <p>
                        Von prioritizes correctness and thoroughness over speed of delivery.
                        Every fix goes through a rigorous quality process before being submitted.
                    </p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Verification:</strong> Confirm the repository builds and tests pass before any changes</li>
                        <li><strong>Evidence Gathering:</strong> Collect logs, error traces, and reproducible test cases</li>
                        <li><strong>Root Cause Analysis:</strong> Identify the true source of the bug, not just symptoms</li>
                        <li><strong>Testing Conventions:</strong> Follow the project's existing test style and frameworks</li>
                        <li><strong>Patch Review:</strong> Check for correctness, behavior preservation, regression risk, code hygiene, security, and maintainer readability</li>
                        <li><strong>New Tests:</strong> Add tests for the fix and run the existing test suite</li>
                        <li><strong>Self-Review:</strong> Reflect on the process and identify improvements for next time</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="demo-note-card">
                    <h2>Runtime Configuration</h2>
                    <p>
                        <strong>Current AgentTargetRunTime:</strong> 10 minutes
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Each Von agent pass runs for up to 10 minutes, allowing deep analysis
                        and thorough work on each subtask before handing off to the next pass.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Von uses a natural-language program execution system with focused child
                        agent passes that plan, run, and hand off work across a structured call stack.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="demo-notes" style="margin-top: 1rem;">
                <div class="demo-note-card">
                    <h2>Find the Owner</h2>
                    <p>Connect with the creator of Von and Sym on social platforms:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/wowo51" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">LinkedIn</a></li>
                        <li><a href="https://github.com/Wowo51" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="demo-note-card">
                    <h2>Payment Options</h2>
                    <p>Von accepts the following payment methods:</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Credit Card:</strong> Standard credit and debit card payments</li>
                        <li><strong>Crypto:</strong> Cryptocurrency payments accepted</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        Contact the owner through the links above to arrange payment for bug fixing services.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</div>

